# MovieHub Development Roadmap

## Project Goal

Build a production-ready Telegram Movie Storage & Distribution Bot using Python, Pyrogram, MongoDB Atlas, FastAPI, and Telegram Database Channels.

The project will be developed incrementally. Every milestone must result in a working, testable application.

